BitcoinJS,is,a,open,source,resource,for,the,development,of,Bitcoin,projects,The,site,provides,libraries,of,Bitcoin,related,code,that,can,be,used,for,mobile,wallet,and,trading,services,The,BitcoinJS,Wallet,Server,API,allows,users,to,synchronize,Bitcoin,wallets,between,multiple,clients,and,devices,and,enhances,security,The,API,accepts,calls,to,create,a,wallet,log,in,to,a,wallet,check,a,pin,add,and,download,items,from,the,wallet,and,several,other,calls